{"tid":2100914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友已經失業左半年","createTime":"2020-07-09T11:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:35:03.000Z","uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f772a3bf42630902165d5c239df249578668edac","tid":2100914,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左已經4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係一齊之前已經知佢未搵倒工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日食屋企遊手好閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭叫過佢去是但搵份part time賺下生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼減輕下佢屋企經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔使永遠出街都我出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(連爆房錢condom錢都係我出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n次次見佢咁頹廢就叫佢認真d搵份工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多兩講就燥左屌返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加佢已經半年冇返過工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日去爆房都係我出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時都係佢插我先 俾佢出左野enjoy左先到我既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最終我今日真係好嬲 我撳住佢插佢出左野就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd25a1c05dbf1bb343960a4de2f06578928d9efc","tid":2100914,"uid":5125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"643d4e26496c4cd0d36433a1d0c012ab799520a0","tid":2100914,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd25a1c05dbf1bb343960a4de2f06578928d9efc","tid":2100914,"uid":5125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"Gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"你係戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}